info: SIPRP V is to provide parallel financing with the World Bank’s poverty reduction support credits (PRSCs) 7–9 within the framework of the PRSC process. Subprogram 1 provided parallel financing with PRSC 7. Subprogram 2 will provide parallel financing with PRSC 8, covering a subset of actions included in the policy matrix for PRSC 8.
name: SUPPORT FOR THE IMPLEM OF THE POVERTY REDUC PROGRAM V (SUBPROG 2)
